name: Kahlil MILLER, Petitioner v. Philadelphia Common Pleas Judge Genece BRINKLEY, Philadelphia Court Of Common Pleas, Respondents

parties: Kahlil MILLER, Petitioner v. Philadelphia Common Pleas Judge Genece BRINKLEY, Philadelphia Court Of Common Pleas, Respondents.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 14th day of May, 2012, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED. The Prothonotary is directed to strike the name of the jurist from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
